		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_UNIT_EXOTIC_UNIT_IROQUIOS_MUSKET_RIDER_STRATEGY">
			<Text>Use the Iroquios Musket Rider to rapidly attack your enemies, then move away to fight another day. They may move after attacking, but receive no defensive bonus from terrain.</Text>
